title: Double Trouble 2022: Titans & Texans
description:
Field Yates, Mike Clay and Daniel Dopp recap Mike’s draft strategy from ESPN’s Live Fantasy Marathon Draft before diving into a Double Trouble on the Titans and Texans. Then, the crew talks some dynasty league planning to round out the show.
